<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 (ltkn ạ̹rạdtk fy ḥyạty yạ yswʿ
 mslmạaⁿ nfsy wqlby fy slạm wkẖḍwʿ)2
 (fạ̉nạ mlk lk mṭmỷn mʿk)2
 tstryḥ nfsy wtfrḥ fy ḥmạk
 dmk ạltẖmyn ykfy llḥmạyh yạ yswʿ
 mn kl sẖr ydnw mny mrwʿạaⁿ nfsy fy kẖwf
 (ạ̉ḥtmy fy ḥḍnk mljạ̉y fy sẖkẖṣk)2
 fslạmy dwmạaⁿ rby bạ̹ltfạfy nḥwk
 (fy bʿdy ʿnk ạ̉sẖʿr bmrạr wsẖjwn
 fy qrby mnk ạ̉hnỷ bslạm wsrwr)2
 (ạ̉sʿd fy qrbk ạ̉ḥzn fy bʿdk)2
 fḥyạty tsmw rby bạ̹qtrạby nḥwk</lyrics>
